---
description: Testing + coverage floor
globs: apps/**/*.ts,libs/**/*.ts
---

Full detail: [docs/agents/testing.md](../../docs/agents/testing.md).

- Every behavioural change ships with tests. Coverage must stay ≥ 90% (jest enforces it).
- Unit specs are co-located `*.spec.ts`, mock all I/O (no real network/DB), cover branches
  and error paths, and have descriptive names.
- e2e (`apps/*/test/**/*.e2e-spec.ts`) boot the real app against a disposable Postgres DB:
  `npm run db:up && npm run e2e:setup && npm run e2e`. Throttling toggled by `THROTTLE_DISABLED`.
- Sensitive routes: extend `apps/api/test/security-owasp.e2e-spec.ts` and run `npm run scan:security`.
- Definition of done: `npm run verify` (+ e2e for logic). When a gate fails, fix the
  code — never lower thresholds, skip tests, or farm coverage with assertion-free tests.
